title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message:
Hi,
2010 2.66 i7 820-2850
MacBook Pro that I replaced the Tandan Cap now Video works fine.
When I plug power into MagSafe Machine starts up.
Keyboard works letters work and trackpad works.
If I push the power button on keyboard machine instantly shutdown. I try to start by pushing power button and nothing happens.
I tried another keyboard and no difference.
Disconnected everything same issue.
?

title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message: Does the charge light turn green when you press the power button ? Basically is it doing a smc reset ?

title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message: Yes charge light turn green when you press the power button

title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message:
Any corrosion on keyboard connector ?

Whats U5000 area like ? Any components knocked off or out of spec ?

title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message: Issue will be around U5001 or U5703, probably corrosion.

title: 2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
message:

U5703 has a burned through pin due to a liquid spill.

2010 MacBook Pro won't start when power button is pushed.
